videos.headline: Spartans QB runs for 61-yard TD
videos.description: Western Michigan defenders chase Michigan State QB Brian Lewerke 61 yards to the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF-One-Play (Spartans QB runs for 61-yard TD) 2017/09/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Western Michigan cashes in on fumble with TD
videos.description: The Broncos force Spartans QB Hunter Rison to fumble and they return the loose ball 67 yards to get on the board in the third quarter.
